title: Make it Your Home Today!!
posting_body: ['This home is just right!', 'Call Today', 'show contact info', 'Ext 300', '~ A must see!', '3 bedroom/2 bath/2 car garage ~~ $1709* per month ~~ Brand new splash pad, pool, park with walking trails, picnic area, playground and more!!', "It's terrible that the prices of rent keep going up!", 'We have a deal for you!', 'We have zero down options available.', '$1,000 get you in your new home and we pay closing costs!!', 'Nothing terrible about this deal!', "The kitchen is chef's dream with the beautiful custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, spacious island, and gorgeous granite countertops!", 'The master suite is fit for a queen!', 'There is a large covered patio for family time or entertaining!', 'Lovely community with that country feel, but conveniences are nearby!', 'Listed here are just a few of the great features:', '• rounded corners', '• stainless steel appliances', '• granite', '• wood floors', '• new carpet', '• landscaping and sod', '• fenced', '• and more', 'Call today', 'show contact info', 'Ext 300', 'and let one of our home consultants guide you through', 'the process of homeownership.', 'Phone calls are preferred.', 'If responding to ad by email please include link to the posting you are inquiring about along with contact information.', '*P&I. $300,900, 5.625% Fixed/6.720% APR, 3.5% Down, FHA 30 year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Price and rates are subject to change without notice.']
